jc.fog.presentation.commands

Class Commands

  • java.lang.Object
    • jc.fog.presentation.commands.Commands

  • public final class Commands
extends Object
    Non-extendable class with Command String constants for use with the FrontController in presentation layer. aka. Constant interface anti-pattern.
    Author:
    Claus
